ZH: 1. 当你看到红灯时，要减速慢行。
EN: When you see a red light, you should slow down and proceed with caution.

ZH: 2. 驾驶员应该根据路况适时减速。
EN: Drivers should slow down according to road conditions.

ZH: 3. 在城市里驾驶时，请注意减速以确保安全。
EN: When driving in the city, remember to slow down to ensure safety.

ZH: 4. 风雪天气驾驶时一定要减速。
EN: It is essential to slow down when driving in windy and snowy weather.

ZH: 5. 快速走道上有许多弯道，因此请减速。
EN: There are many sharp turns on the fast lane, so please slow down.

ZH: 6. 驾驶员需要提前减速准备停车。
EN: Drivers need to slow down in advance to prepare for parking.

ZH: 7. 在学校附近要减速，以防意外。
EN: Slow down near the school to prevent accidents.

ZH: 8. 雨天请不要忘记减速，以确保行车安全。
EN: Don't forget to slow down on rainy days to ensure safe driving.

ZH: 9. 当看到行人横过马路时，请立即减速。
EN: When you see pedestrians crossing the road, slow down immediately.

ZH: 10. 驾驶员要遵守交通规则，不得在高速路上超速，需时刻减速。
EN: Drivers must obey traffic rules, not speeding on the highway, and always slow down.

ZH: 11. 遇到交通堵塞时，请适时减速以避免追尾。
EN: When encountering traffic congestion, slow down in time to avoid rear-end collisions.

ZH: 12. 在狭窄的道路上行驶时请减速。
EN: Slow down when driving on narrow roads.

ZH: 13. 遇到不熟悉的路段请及时减速，避免发生意外。
EN: Slow down in unfamiliar road sections to prevent accidents.

ZH: 14. 在转弯之前请减速减速，以免侧滑。
EN: Slow down before turning to prevent skidding.

ZH: 15. 车辆在山区行驶时一定要减速以避免危险。
EN: Vehicles must slow down when driving in mountainous areas to avoid danger.

ZH: 16. 遇到紧急情况时请立即减速做出应急反应。
EN: Slow down and react promptly in case of emergencies.

ZH: 17. 在施工路段请不要超速，减速行驶。
EN: Do not speed in construction zones, slow down instead.

ZH: 18. 在弯道处要减速以避免车辆失控。
EN: Slow down in curves to avoid losing control of the vehicle.

ZH: 19. 驾驶员在市区内要注意减速，以免冲突。
EN: Drivers should pay attention to slowing down in urban areas to avoid conflicts.

ZH: 20. 遇到突发事件要第一时间减速，确保安全。
EN: Slow down immediately in case of emergencies to ensure safety.
